- Ohh, double do-do!

13:04.350 --> 13:05.470
What's up, doc?

13:05.610 --> 13:08.310
One of my diamonds
just fell in the macaroni.

13:10.030 --> 13:12.270
Kenickie, want a piece of salami?

13:12.410 --> 13:15.030
