If I eat that, I'll smell like you.

13:15.160 --> 13:16.780
What a stink!

13:16.910 --> 13:18.490
Hey, guys, look.

13:20.370 --> 13:23.830
Ladies and gentlemen,
dingleberries on parade.

13:25.710 --> 13:29.300
Look! You really put
your foot into it this time.

13:29.430 --> 13:32.000
Try hopscotch, you hot dog.

13:32.970 --> 13:35.970
What a gavone! Gumdrops, man.

13:39.440 --> 13:42.640
Any of you guys see
that new chick in registration?

13:42.780 --> 13:44.850
Sure beats
the foam domes round here.

13:44.990 --> 13:46.610
Jugs bigger than Annette's?

13:46.740 --> 13:50.030
Nobody's jugs
are bigger than Annette's.

13:54.870 --> 13:57.000
Hey, guys. Hey!

14:00.300 --> 14:01.920
Hi, girls.

14:02.380 --> 14:04.210
You're a sick man, Putz.

14:07.600 --> 14:10.680
Hey, I wanna hear about
what Danny did at the beach.

14:11.350 --> 14:14.850
- It was nothing.
- Sure, nothing, Zuko. Right?

14:14.980 --> 14:18.070
- You got in her drawers, right?
- Come on, tell us.

14:18.190 --> 14:19.650
What did you do this summer?

14:19.780 --> 14:23.060
I spent most of it at the beach.
I met a boy there.

14:23.200 --> 14:25.900
You hauled your cookies
to the beach for a guy?

14:26.040 --> 14:29.410
- He was sorta special.
- There ain't no such thing.

14:30.750 --> 14:32.210
It was really romantic.

14:32.330 --> 14:34.660
Everything about it.

14:34.800 --> 14:37.710
You don't want to hear
the horny details.

14:37.840 --> 14:39.470
Alright, I'll tell you.

