19:12.210 --> 19:14.370
Way to go, red and white

19:14.500 --> 19:16.960
Go Rydell, fight, fight, fight!

19:18.170 --> 19:21.260
(fanfare)

19:25.060 --> 19:26.880
And now...

19:27.520 --> 19:29.810
Quiet, please.

19:32.650 --> 19:36.810
Quiet, everyone. Now, boys and girls,
the man of the hour.

19:36.950 --> 19:38.770
The coach we're all depending on

19:38.910 --> 19:42.440
to pull Rydell out of
a seven-season slump,

19:42.580 --> 19:45.370
our very own Coach Calhoun.

19:45.500 --> 19:47.330
(cheering)

19:55.090 --> 19:57.760
- Who's the best?
- (all) Rydell!

20:00.390 --> 20:02.470
